{"tid":676141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［真係黐線］男子潛入長安邨單位被制服 揭發為特遣隊警員","createTime":"2018-05-24T06:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T15:51:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e06818a11dfce98fe3facf00d185cc4ae2a9d69f","tid":676141,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"【13:45】消息指，涉案男子為一名特遣隊警員，為該大廈住客，暫時未知他於案發時是否正在當值，重案組探員正調查他現身單位的原因【10:25】葵青警區重案組接手調查<br />\n<br />\n早上7時半，青衣長安邨安湄樓發生爆竊案。男女住戶外出後因事折返，不料大門虛掩，赫見一名陌生男子大模施樣坐在客廳，懷疑他潛入爆竊，連忙將他截住及報警。警方在疑人身上沒有搜到可疑物品或屬於屋主的物件，現正在場調查，列爆竊案處理，疑人事後被警方帶走調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/143859_e0968dade165ef2899e8592f74307f9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F143859_e0968dade165ef2899e8592f74307f9b.png&h=207bbf92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/143901_cc688569a8e9e8389339b7f5874ae042.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F143901_cc688569a8e9e8389339b7f5874ae042.png&h=14bb33f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 ：63836568<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180524/58230510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58230510&d=C6%2FwMpxvgzXTcJaCSL%2FEcf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e78939c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58230510&h=32e22b8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180524/58230510</a>"},{"pid":"0c9d7d289bdd3bc491c0e5a39f9ff932f603b4b3","tid":676141,"uid":144843,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d9fd7723d6d1dc0be87f24a26dbc47c5d343af6","tid":676